name: Dina Diefenbach
text: Made fresh right in front of you.  Price is good and there is a good selection to choose from.  They make sure you know how to cook it before you leave the store.  Directions are included with the pizza.  They carry tubs of chocolate chip cookie dough as well.

name: Dianna Gross
text: Might have a little wait but good staff & pizza is always delicious

name: Tessica Oehler
text: This business is closed down. Drove all the way here to find empty building.

name: Jeff Graha
text: Long story, short. Cashier man needs additional training. Waited 15 minutes, still no one making my pizza, when I asked about my pizza, I was notified that the pizza maker man had a bad case of diahrea and would be with me shorty. My refund was in the form of cash.

name: Michelle Clawson
text:
